descriptionHtml:
Small mod improved Jenassa (companion and wife) from Whiterun

Install:
1. Unzip steamapps\\common\\skyrim\\Data
2. Activate in NMM or Skyrim Launcher 

Unistall:
1. Just delete from steamapps\\common\\skyrim\\Data file Improved Jenassa.esp

Other mods used:
1. http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=2812 - Better Females by Bella
2. http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=5162 - Daedric female armor replacer by MaikCG
author: bot2b
